The '''Senate Head of Public Affairs''' was the senior [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]] [[Bureaucrat/Legends|bureaucrat]] responsible for public relations at the [[Senate Head of Public Affairs Office]].

[[Mar Rugeyan]] held the position during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].

